<expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒu vveinſperg </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l34">von des geleÿts <expan>vveg<ex>en</ex></expan> ut in
                        forma / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_226_r1l36">Antvvurt beÿ <expan>vnſ<ex>erm</ex></expan>
