                                <expan>vvid<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>cʒuvviſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_227_r1l5">beÿ diſem <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in die
