<div type="addressee">
<ab>Burgraf Johansen; <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Sawnsheim von
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Hans<ex>en</ex></expan> von Hohenlochs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>;
                        bischof von <expan>Wirczb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>w<ex>er</ex></expan> czu <expan>dis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan> sein gewalt hat; Johan, graf zu Wertheim;
                        Hanman <expan>Echt<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>vicztu<ex>m</ex></expan> czu
                                <expan>Aschaffenb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
</ab>
